    "Using each group, we model claim frequency and claim severity separately and multiply the results to calculate the risk premium.",
    "We utilise the duration (measured in days) as an exposure metric and use it to standardise the claim frequency.",
    "For example, if a policyholder has their policy for half a year and incurs one claim, it will be recorded as two claims when standardised and viewed over a full year of exposure.",
